text: Christopher George (born December 25, 1983) is a judoka from Trinidad and Tobago. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's 100 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the second round by Yan Naing Soe. ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Trinidad and Tobago male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Trinidad and Tobago Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Judoka at the 2015 Pan American Games
